aces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重溫經典<br />\n林太豪氣回應，「290萬已經最低，我個仔買貴40萬冇咩問題，佢要住㗎嘛，如果升又點呢。阿仔買嘅單位，銀行估到價，銀行唔會死錯人嘅，嗰啲咁既專家，食屎啦！我哋唔係有見地，我哋係腳踏實地，唔聽專家㗎，聽專家意見就死啦。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170308/19950864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170308%2F19950864&d=QityVE64U90TG%2BhHdk7iNb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1b8c688b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170308%2F19950864&h=1154b792\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20170308/19950864</a>"},{"pid":"5742f69f6a55c1b996dda20f6c960a5125c2b315","tid":499460,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T23:27:09.000Z","msg":"上一個post<br />\n<br />\n【聖誕加息機會高】低調置業討論區(87)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/492308/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/492308/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c3459e5580afd58dd7cd8d4193cd70b20a40d6df","tid":499460,"uid":83840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"8a6e8798ee037e64fb19690b4d369bb79fa90abc","tid":499460,"uid":8957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T00:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngrant loan好似count架喎<br />\n我之前申請boc，佢都有問我</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0312eac30f831325b3